                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        <a href="/" title="The Ghost Pubs website">www.GhostPubs.com</a>
                                    </p>
                                </div>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-group">
                        <div class="accordion-heading">
                            <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseSeven">
                                I can write a ghost story about a pub for Ghost Pubs - how can Ghost Pubs help?
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseSeven" class="accordion-body collapse" style="height: 0;">
                            <div class="accordion-inner">
                                <div class="well well-large">
                                    <p>
                                        Hello there,
                                    </p>

                                    <p>
                                        We officially launched Ghost Pubs on Halloween 2013. We have not yet covered every haunted public house.
                                        Indeed, the usefulness of our website depends upon contributions from our perspective readers.
                                        Yes, that's you! So, please feel free to send us any ghostly information about public houses that you have visited. For full coverage, it all rests on your contributions.
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        Please send us your story as soon as possible through <a href="https://twitter.com/ghost_pubs">twitter</a> or <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/ghostpubs/">facebook</a>. You'll receive full credit and you may win a prize.
